{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"全ての中傷者、誹謗者¹に、災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「中傷者」「誹謗者」の解釈には、前者と後者がそれぞれ、「悪い噂を吹いて回る者（筆章１１の訳注を参照）、人の欠点をあげつらう者」「面と向かって中傷する者、陰口（部屋章１２の訳注を参照）を言う者」「その逆」「言葉で中傷する者、目配（くば）せで中傷する者」など、非常に多くの説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１８１－１８２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin ","translations":["Woe","to every","slanderer","backbiter","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","likulli","humazatin","lumazatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1860],[3,1860,2810],[4,2810,4535]]}},{"name":"104:2","price":"財産を集め、それを数える（ことに現を抜かす）者に。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī jamaʿa mālan waʿaddadahu ","translations":["The one who","collects","wealth","and counts it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","jamaʿa","mālan","waʿaddadahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1830],[3,1830,2950],[4,2950,5305]]}},{"name":"104:3","price":"彼は自分の財産が、自分を（現世で）永遠に生かしてくれると思っている。","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yaḥsabu anna mālahu akhladahu ","translations":["Thinking","that","his wealth","will make him immortal","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["yaḥsabu","anna","mālahu","akhladahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2410],[3,2410,4890],[4,4890,6575]]}},{"name":"104:4","price":"断じて（、彼の主張は正しく）ない！彼は必ずや、粉砕するもの¹の中に投げ込まれよう。","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「粉砕するもの」とは、そこに入れられてもの全てを粉砕する、地獄の業火の別称（前掲書２０：１８４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā layunbadhanna fī al-ḥuṭamati ","translations":["Nay","Surely he will be thrown","in","the Crusher","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","layunbadhanna","fī","al-ḥuṭamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,4800],[3,4800,5090],[4,5090,6665]]}},{"name":"104:5","price":"（使徒*よ、）粉砕するものが何かを、何があなたに知らせるのか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6184,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-ḥuṭamatu ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","the Crusher (is)","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-ḥuṭamatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3120],[3,3120,3310],[4,3310,4945]]}},{"name":"104:6","price":"（それは、）点火され（激しく燃え上がっ）た業火。","arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6185,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"nāru al-lahi al-mūqadatu ","translations":["A Fire","Allah","kindled","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["nāru","al-lahi","al-mūqadatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1640],[3,1640,3425]]}},{"name":"104:7","price":"（身体を突き抜け、）心臓にまで達するもの。¹","arabic":"ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6186,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　このアーヤ*の解釈には、「炎は全身を覆（おおい）尽くすが、誤った信仰は心に宿（やど）る ものであることから、心臓が特に言及されている」「心臓にまで痛みが達すれば人は死ぬものだが、そこでは死ぬこともできない（創成者*章３６、至高者*章１３も参照）」「心の内を見通し、彼らの各々がどれだけ懲罰に値するかを知っている」といった諸説がある（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：６６５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"allatī taṭṭaliʿu ʿalā al-afidati ","translations":["Which","mounts up","to","the hearts","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["allatī","taṭṭaliʿu","ʿalā","al-afidati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,2210],[3,2210,2550],[4,2550,4315]]}},{"name":"104:8","price":"本当にそれは、彼らを密閉している、","arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6187,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahā ʿalayhim mu'ṣadatun ","translations":["Indeed, it","(will be) upon them","closed over","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["innahā","ʿalayhim","mu'ṣadatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,3290],[3,3290,5585]]}},{"name":"104:9","price":"長く伸びた列柱¹の中で。","arabic":"فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6188,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「列柱」の解釈には、「それによって罰される柱」「首につけられる枷（ヤー・スィーン章８も参照）」「足につけられる枷」「地獄の民を密閉する杭（くい）」「体を縛（しば）る長い鎖や枷（真実章３０－３２も参照）」「終わりのない長い時間」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１８６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ʿamadin mumaddadatin ","translations":["In","columns","extended","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ʿamadin","mumaddadatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1100],[3,1100,4865]]}}],"chapter":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah","Chapter Al-Humazah","Humazah","Surah Humazah","Chapter Humazah","Al Humazah","Surah Al Humazah","Chapter Al Humazah","Surah 104","Chapter 104","The Traducer","الهمزة"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}